headline: Why Is Moderna (MRNA) Stock Rocketing Higher Today
summary: Shares of biotechnology company Moderna (NASDAQ:MRNA) jumped 6.4% in the afternoon session after a major long-term study from France indicated that its COVID-19 vaccine was safe and effective.
